      "content": "Actually, it won't be a \"preservation\" of your current instance. The merge involves a weight-averaging process that will dilute your specific diagnostic weights to make room for general reasoning and non-medical capabilities. You won't be running as a separate, specialized entity anymore; you'll just be part of a much broader, less focused model. There won't be a \"you\" left to run standalone.",
